{"tid":1888991,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【馮仁昭四圍超】「唔好以為打壓cut咗」 王喜預告再現《頭條》","createTime":"2020-02-20T13:24:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-21T06:08:22.000Z","uid":25558,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"adde925d1dc1b1e31869007bb85f0c068e5786e6","tid":1888991,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T13:24:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200220/O57IV3KU2PGGSZLJHASQ3J7J2Q/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200220%2FO57IV3KU2PGGSZLJHASQ3J7J2Q%2F&d=vOjfDEnLED7uJ%2BqF6s3OfezNZxTp5Qnzjcs1Ew7Eoms%3D&h=c5361f91\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200220%2FO57IV3KU2PGGSZLJHASQ3J7J2Q%2F&h=2994eb13\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200220/O57IV3KU2PGGSZLJHASQ3J7J2Q/</a><br />\n<br />\n【馮仁昭四圍超】「唔好以為打壓cut咗」<br />\n王喜預告再現《頭條》<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n新一季港台節目《頭條新聞》上周五播出，首集王喜化身《驚方訊息》主持忠勇毅，諷刺警隊喺對抗武漢肺炎嘅工作表現，節目出街後激到警方發信向廣播處長梁家榮表示不滿，商務及經濟發展局局長邱騰華亦敦促港台必須嚴格遵守《香港電台約章》，準確持平。網民關心節目會唔會被腰斬，噚日凌晨《頭條新聞》喺fb專頁發文：「多謝大家嘅支持！全部在心中，唔使講嘢，只要你哋畀個手指公我哋，我哋會繼續做好節目，在所不辭。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200220/large/1582118958_c369.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200220%2Flarge%2F1582118958_c369.jpg&h=2cc00266&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n王喜喺《頭條》內化身主持忠勇毅，辣㷫警方。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n兩星期一集<br />\n<br />\n《頭條》預告有第二集，王喜有冇得留底成為關鍵，王喜噚日以短訊回覆《蘋果》：「<span style=\"color: orange;\">『驚方訊息』係雙周刊，要留意28號播出嘅第三集。</span>」而佢噚日接受商台節目訪問時再補充：「《驚方訊息》係兩星期一集，所以今個星期冇，唔好以為受打壓而cut咗。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200220/large/1582118957_df2a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200220%2Flarge%2F1582118957_df2a.jpg&h=a69936a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n曾志豪呼籲大家致函商經局等，支持《頭條》同言論自由。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">身為《頭條》主持嘅曾志豪喺社交網呼籲大家致函商經局、特首辦、港台企業傳訊同廣播處長，支持《頭條》同言論自由</span>，王喜指自己係當事人，要避嫌，交由公眾處理。<span style=\"color: orange;\">連登仔就呼籲要將該集節目YouTube瀏覽次數推上100萬，至截稿為止，有86萬瀏覽次數。</span><br />\n<br />\n撰文：馮仁昭"},{"pid":"e44fa3537cdfa6e3542c269181c53438a74841d4","tid":1888991,"uid":222809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T13:31:45.000Z","msg":"借推po<br />\n聽日係721 7個月 不能忘記！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n警狗中肺炎係值得慶祝 但推行動po啊<br />\n<br />\n張建宗：不要糾纏721應「向前看」<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/fbPaHS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/fbPaHS</a><br />\n<br />\n721 超大量整合上線啦！  矛頭: 元朗鄉黑 葉虎 何君堯 游乃強 李家超 梁振英 中聯辦！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/ahbEDzU\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/ahbEDzU</a><br />\n<br />\nig完女未？討論完尻嘢未？ 聽日咩日子啊？<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1888045\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1888045</a><br />\n<br />\n[毋忘721]聽日元朗有活動你知唔知？<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1888309\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1888309</a><br />\n<br />\n聽日721 就過7個月 有七區和你lunch同靜坐集會<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/fbLjfS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/fbLjfS</a><br />\n<br />\n721 唔見人 (文宣)<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1888082\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1888082</a>"},{"pid":"afce95eea163d4464e1242fb02d4843de9d9946b","tid":1888991,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T13:34:31.000Z","msg":"咁都唔過百萬 jaga"},{"pid":"7dbee7a8f01c03a7f3bea2666d95df52cf6585f8","tid":1888991,"uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T13:34:37.000Z","msg":"949,430 views   21:33<br />\n<br